(142, 17, 20, '11) Multiple Accounts And Rewards', '11-multiple-accounts-and-rewards', '<p>We allow you to have multiple accounts in Opportunity \"4\". Why? We have some amazing rewards in Opportunity \"4\", we allow you to have as many accounts as you can to allow you to have access to as many as rewards you chose to have! Amazing, right? Read this to see the amazing rewards awaiting for you!<br></p>', 'COURSE', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/pages/multiple-accounts-and-rewards-in-opportunity-4?id=', 0.00, 'ONE TIME', 'YES', NULL, '2019-09-04 01:56:20', '2019-09-04 01:56:20', 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/uploads/thumbnails/20190903_215620_Multiple Accounts and Rewards in Opportunity 4. Engl.jpg'),
(143, 18, 21, '11) Pluralite de Comptes et Recompenses', '11-pluralite-de-comptes-et-recompenses', '<p>Nous vous permettons d\'avoir plusieurs comptes dans Opportunité \"4\". Pourquoi? Nous avons des récompenses incroyables dans Opportunity \"4\". Nous vous permettons d’avoir autant de comptes que vous pouvez pour vous permettre d’avoir accès à autant de récompenses que vous avez choisi avoir! Incroyable, non? Lisez ceci pour voir les incroyables récompenses qui vous attendent!<br></p>', 'COURSE', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/pages/pluralite-de-comptes-et-recompenses-dans-opportunity-4?id=', 0.00, 'ONE TIME', 'YES', NULL, '2019-09-04 01:59:49', '2019-09-04 02:01:12', 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/uploads/thumbnails/20190903_220112_Multiple Accounts and Rewards in Opportunity 4. fR.jpg'),
(146, 17, 20, '12) Why The Total Of The Fees Is Not Mentioned In Our Calculation', '12-why-the-total-of-the-fees-is-not-mentioned-in-our-calculation', '<p>Why the total of the fees is not used when calculating the commissions? Is there any reason? What is that reason? Read this to know!<br></p>', 'COURSE', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/pages/why-taxes-are-not-included-in-commissions-calculations?id=', 0.00, 'ONE TIME', 'YES', NULL, '2019-09-04 02:28:12', '2019-09-04 02:33:11', 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/uploads/thumbnails/20190903_223311_Why taxes are not included in commissions calculation.Engl.jpg'),
(145, 18, 21, '12) Pourquoi le total des frais pas utilise dans le calcul des commissions', '12-pourquoi-le-total-des-frais-pas-utilise-dans-le-calcul-des-commissions', '<p>Pourquoi le total des frais n\'est-il pas utilisé dans le calcul des commissions? Y a-t-il une raison? Quelle est cette raison? Lisez ceci pour en savoir plus!<br></p>', 'COURSE', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/pages/pourquoi-ne-mentionnons-nous-pas-les-taxes-dans-nos-calculs-des-commissions?id=', 0.00, 'ONE TIME', 'YES', NULL, '2019-09-04 02:21:26', '2019-09-04 02:21:26', 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/uploads/thumbnails/20190903_222126_Why taxes are not included in commissions calculation.FR.jpg'),
(147, 17, 20, '13) Do not waste time after registration', '13-do-not-waste-time-after-registration', '<p>Do not waste time after registration! How can you easily do this? It is by not understanding how the system works! Avoid this by reading&nbsp;this!<br></p>', 'COURSE', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/pages/do-not-waste-your-time-after-registration?id=', 0.00, 'ONE TIME', 'YES', NULL, '2019-09-04 04:39:36', '2019-09-04 04:39:36', 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/uploads/thumbnails/20190904_003936_Do not waste your time after registration.Engl.jpg'),
(148, 18, 21, '13) Ne perd pas le temps apres inscription', '13-ne-perd-pas-le-temps-apres-inscription', '<p>Ne perd pas le temps après inscription! Comment pouvez-vous facilement faire ceci? C\'est en ne comprenant pas comment le système fonctionne! Evitez cela en lisant ceci!<br></p>', 'COURSE', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/pages/ne-perdez-pas-votre-temps-apres-inscription?id=', 0.00, 'ONE TIME', 'YES', NULL, '2019-09-04 04:42:52', '2019-09-04 04:42:52', 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/uploads/thumbnails/20190904_004252_Do not waste your time after registration.Fr.jpg'),
(149, 17, 20, '14) Do you know you are an entrepreneur after your registration', '14-do-you-know-you-are-an-entrepreneur-after-your-registration', '<p>Do you know that you became an entrepreneur the very second you registered on Opportunity 4. You are an entrepreneur and you have an entreprise to develop, to improve, to make succeed.&nbsp;And we are going to assist you doing that! Read this to learn more.<br></p>', 'COURSE', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/pages/do-you-know-you-become-an-entrepreneur-after-you-register-in-opportunity-4?id=', 0.00, 'ONE TIME', 'YES', NULL, '2019-09-04 05:01:43', '2019-09-04 05:01:43', 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/uploads/thumbnails/20190904_010143_Do you know you become an entrepreneur after you register in Opportunity 4.Fr.jpg'),
(150, 18, 21, '14) Savez-vous que vous etes devenu entrepreneur', '14-savez-vous-que-vous-etes-devenu-entrepreneur', '<p>Vous êtes un entrepreneur après votre inscription dans Opportunité \"4\". Qu\'est-ce que cela vous demande de faire? Découvrez-le en lisant ceci!<br></p>', 'COURSE', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/pages/vous-etes-un-entrepreneur-quand-vous-vous-inscrivez-dans-opportunity-4?id=', 0.00, 'ONE TIME', 'YES', NULL, '2019-09-04 05:05:30', '2019-09-04 05:05:30', 'https://www.dnasbookdigimarketafrica.com/uploads/thumbnails/20190904_010530_Do you know you become an entrepreneur after you register in Opportunity 4.Engl.jpg');
