r\n<p>DNAsbook General, LLC is an entrepreneurship training and financing company based in America. To be a distributor of its training and funding (Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo;), you just have to follow instructions we are going to give you, there is no special level of education required. Here are the conditions to fulfill to be qualified:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1) You can be from any country provided you speak or understand English or French (one of our 2 languages ​​used at Opportunity 4 for the moment).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2) Be able to go in front of people and talk to them in a convincing way. Communication and explanation skills are required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3) Register on our site.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4) There is a mandatory training: Before you can have access to the registration page, you must go through an online training (required). We think you just cannot distribute something you don&rsquo;t understand!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5) Apply our 20/20 Rule (this is mandatory for Opportunity 4 to pay your monthly fees for you through your monthly commissions).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6) Your information on your Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo; account must be true, accurate and always updated. In case of false information, you will be solely responsible for any errors resulting from it, for example in the case of your commissions being sent to a wrong address or in the case of being not able to communicate with you through email or phone. Opportunity &ldquo;4&rdquo; will not be responsible for such errors if they are due to You, choosing to put wrong and false information on your account or not updating your account information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>NOTES: On cell phones, after you click &quot;next&quot;, the system could bring you back to this text again to make sure you are not a robot. If this happens, just click the button &quot;next&quot; again and the system will let you have access to a 4h 56 minute training video that you have to watch entirely to have access to the registration page. This training is compulsory, mandatory!</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Once again, on the video page, you have to watch the entire video, that is your important training before you can register. After you watch this training video entirely and click the button &quot;I have watched the entire video&quot;, if the system does not let you advance to the registration page, clean the page, go back to our Ads, click again the button &quot;Learn more&quot; under our Ads or click on the link of this page you saved and click &ldquo;next&rdquo; button and&nbsp; the system will let you access the registration page directly.&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>This happens only on cell phones just to make sure you are not a robot. On a desktop computer, the system lets you move on more quickly.</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>After registration, keep your username and password jealously and safely. Your affiliate link is very important. Copy your affiliate link and save it. You will see your affiliate link on your dashboard, just above the welcome video. Keep your affiliate link jealously because it is that link you will use to register people into your group as the training will clearly tell you.</strong></em></p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-06-26 16:59:33', '2019-10-08 22:13:33', 'en'),
