(36, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'How can you never pay monthly fees in Opportunity 4', 'how-can-you-never-pay-monthly-fees-in-opportunity-4', '<p>How can you never pay monthly fees in Opportunity \"4\"?</p><p>It is by applying Rule 20/20 before the end of the month you register in Opportunity \"4\". If you subscribe into the system 20 people before the end of the month you register into Opportunity \"4\" and all of them pay their fees at the end of the month, you will never pay monthly fees in the system. Why?<br>The monthly fee is 1000 FCFA. If you look at the 1st month commission, it is 2000 FCFA. At which condition? If you bring in the system 20 people and if they pay their fees at the end of the month.</p><p>Let\'s look at it closer! At the end of the month you enter Opportunity \"4\", you will pay 1 000 FCFA. If you succeed subscribing into the system 20 people before the end of the month and they pay their fees at the end of the month, your commission is 2 000 FCFA. What this means?</p><p>This means that you receive 2 amounts of the monthly fee. We reinburse you then the 1 000 FCFA you pay at the end of the month and we give you another 1 000 FCFA for the next month. If you continue applying Rule 20/20, see in the calculation below what will be your commissions in the next months after your first month in the system! Nobody needs to tell you that the system will be generating for you huge monthly commissions to pay for monthly fees!</p><h3>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;The Most Important Secret of Success in Opportunity \"4\"</h3><h3>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; The secret of success in Opportunity \"4\" is the Rule 20/20</h3><h3>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp