(51, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Do you know you become an entrepreneur after you register in Opportunity 4', 'do-you-know-you-become-an-entrepreneur-after-you-register-in-opportunity-4', '<p>Do you know you are an entrepreneur when you register in Opportunity \"4\"?</p><p>Many of you don’t know you become an entrepreneur when you register in Opportunity “4”! Yes, you are an entrepreneur when you register on Opportunity “4”! You have created a company from the time you put your information in Opportunity 4!&nbsp;</p><p>As you earn the huge monthly \"Opportunity 4\" commissions, we train you as an entrepreneur by showing you how to run your business once you become a member of Opportunity \"4\".</p><p>This training is designed to show you how to maximize your commissions in Opportunity \"4\", how to manage your business Opportunity \"4\", how to think and behave as an entrepreneur, how to develop your own business ideas and opportunities, how to pursue your dreams and develop your talents and get you started!&nbsp;</p><p>As you can see, this program takes beginners and turns them into entrepreneurs and finance them!</p><p>We have 2 important features on our sites that are very important for you as entrepreneur:&nbsp;<br>1) A&nbsp;page where you can expose your business to your potentiential subscribers and tell them why they should join your group, why they should work with you. This page also helps you&nbsp;connect to your subscribers on social media. Use it fully!<br>2) A message center that allows you to be in communication with your subscribers. This is vital for your group because to coach the members of your group you need to communicate with them and it is appropriate if it is done within Opportunity \"4\"! Use this message center fully to advance your business within Opportunity \"4\"!</p><p>Do you know that if you have means, you should have an office as businessman? Specially if you want to lead in Opportunity \"4\", you need an office with all its ingredients to help your subscribers. You will &nbsp;meet people who will need your help to start in Opportunity \"4\", you need to invite them into your&nbsp;office to help them! As an entrepreneur, to be performent, you need an office!</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', NULL, '2019-09-02 22:42:37', '2019-09-02 22:42:37', 'en'),
