(57, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'DNAsbook Webinar Questions', 'dnasbook-webinar-questions', '<h4><strong><em>Notes</em>:</strong> <em>To access the registration page, you have to answer the following questions correctly!</em></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1) What is Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) It is a country located in America.<br />\r\nb) It is an Entrepreneurship Network that trains its subscribers in entrepreneurship and finances them.<br />\r\nc) It is an association of American donors that assists poor people worldwide.<br />\r\nd) It is an american company that helps people worldwide.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2) What is the difference between &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; and &quot;Opportunity &quot;4&quot;&quot;?<br />\r\na) They are the same<br />\r\nb) &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; is included in &quot;Opportunity &quot;4&quot;&quot;.<br />\r\nc) &quot;DNAsbook General&quot;, &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; and &quot;Opportunity &quot;4&quot;&quot; are the same, they deal with the same things.<br />\r\nd) &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; is a section of &quot;DNAsbook General&quot;. &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; is reserved for entrepreneurship and financing. &quot;Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is a module of &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot;, it is so important that it is not a mistake to confond it with &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3) What is Rule 20/20?<br />\r\na) It is not that important in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nb) It is a secret, nobody knows what it is.<br />\r\nc) It is a very important rule in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. You have to apply Rule 20/20 if you want to succeed in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nd) It is a rule that was invented and previously used in another company, later adapted to Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4) Why 4 levels of benefit in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) There are 4 levels in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; to help subscribers maximize their monthly commissions because the goal of Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is to help its subscribers financially while training them in entrepreneurship.<br />\r\nb) Because 4 levels are just a better way to do things.<br />\r\nc) Just to distract from the main objective of Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nd) It is to organize things in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. To be honest, nobody know why!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5) How to apply Rule 20/20?<br />\r\na) Just bring 40 people in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; and you have applied Rule 20/20!<br />\r\nb) Applying Rule 20/20 means to bring 20 people into Opportunity &quot;4&quot; through your affiliate link and ask each of them to bring into Opportunity &quot;4&quot;, in their turn, 20 people through their affiliate links and make sure everybody does the same thing till the 4th level.<br />\r\nc) If to talk to 20 people about Opportunity &quot;4&quot; and ask each of them to talk to 20 other people about Opportunity &quot;4&quot;, whether they subscribe or not, you have applied Rule 20/20.<br />\r\nd) Applying Rule 20/20 means subscribing 20 people into Opportunity &quot;4&quot; and stop. You don&#39;t need to do anything else, you finish your job as a distributor of Opportunity &quot;4&quot; training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6) How Opportunity &quot;4&quot; pays your fees?<br />\r\na) When you send them a letter explaining that you are poor, you cannot pay your monthly fees and tell them not to be greedy, they have to pay your monthly fees.<br />\r\nb) By sending you every month a check clearly labeled: &quot;For your monthly fees&quot;.<br />\r\nc) Don&#39;t worry, they send it automatically every month. They know you don&#39;t have money but you want to earn money. They are kind people, they help people wordwide financially.<br />\r\nd) From the time you have 10 subscribers in your group, from level 1 to level 4, Opportunity &quot;4&quot; will begin paying for you your monthly fees through your monthly commissions if these 10 subscribers are active paying their monthly fees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7) How can you never pay monthly fees from your pocket in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) This happens when you tell them that you want them to allow you to never pay monthly fees in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. Do you know, they are kind people, they will listen to you specially when they like you.<br />\r\nb) This happens when you bring into Opportunity &quot;4&quot; 20 people before the end of the month you enter Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. And these 20 people have to be active bringing into Opportunity &quot;4&quot; other people and paying their monthly fees. If you do this, you will have enough commissions right from the 1st month to cover your monthly fees.<br />\r\nc) Opportunity &quot;4&quot; training in entrepreneurship and financing is free, don&#39;t worry about paying monthly fees.<br />\r\nd) Just bring into Opportunity &quot;4&quot; 10 people in your 1st month.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8) What is multiple accounts in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) It is to keep you busy.<br />\r\nb) It is to distract you.<br />\r\nc) Don&#39;t worry! It is nothing!<br />\r\nd) There are challenges and rewards in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. There are multiples accounts in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; to allow subscribers to have access to multiple chances, to unlimited chances to have rewards in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. This allows everybody to have an unlimited chance to earn in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; no matter when you enter Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. There will be always space for everybody because chances to earn in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; are unlimited because of the multiple accounts feature.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9) How Opportunity &quot;4&quot; works?<br />\r\na) There is no rules in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nb) Opportunity &quot;4&quot; has 4 profit levels. Applying Rule 20/20, subscribers have to bring 20 subscribers into the system and ask them to also bring 20 subscribers in the system in their turn. This message has to be passed from subscriber to subscriber till the 4th level and the monthly fees have to be paid by every subscriber.<br />\r\nc) Nobody knows how Opportunity &quot;4&quot; works!<br />\r\nd) Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is just a good Opportunity, isn&#39;t it?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10) Why there are monthly fees in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) Opportunity &quot;4&quot; is a training in entrepreneurship and financing. This important service has a monthly fee because monthly commissions come from the fees paid by subscribers for the service rendered to them. Opportunity &quot;4&quot; decides to share these fees with its subscribers. Commissions come from the fees paid into the system, then fees have to be paid for commissions to be paid.<br />\r\nb) We don&#39;t know. Do you?<br />\r\nc) The system has to be supported and because subscribers have money and they are generous, they have to pay fees.<br />\r\nd) It is to help poor Americans.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11) How to subscribe people into your group in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) Just call them and they come to you!<br />\r\nb) By talking to them and sharing with them the daily good news from America.<br />\r\nc) To subscribe somebody into your group in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;, you have to give him your affiliate link. The person has to click on your affiliate link, follow the instructions and subscribe at the end. This person will be then at your level 1.<br />\r\nd) Don&#39;t worry! Just send the person to the site!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>12) On what subscribers Opportunity &quot;4&quot; pays you?<br />\r\na) On all subscribers in the whole Opportunity &quot;4&quot;. They all belong to you.<br />\r\nb) Opportunity &quot;4&quot; does not pay subscribers only for the people they enroll in the system, they are also paid for subscribers their subscribers enroll into the system up to the 4th level.<br />\r\nc) There is no commission payments in Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nd) They pay you only for people on your 1st level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13) What are the 2 things you need to do in Opportunity &quot;4&quot; to succeed quickly?<br />\r\na) Subscribe 20 people and give them on daily basis some American news.<br />\r\nb) Knowing how to talk to people convincely and pay monthly their fees.<br />\r\nc) Send WhatSapp messages to your friends about Opportunity &quot;4&quot; and nothing else.<br />\r\nd) 1) Apply Rule 20/20 subscribing 20 people into the system through your affiliate link.<br />\r\n2) Ask them to subscribe 20 people into Opportunity &quot;4&quot; in their turn and make sure they pass the same message to each subscriber till&nbsp;the 4th level. Everybody has to pay their monthly fees into the system because commissions come from the fees paid into the system for the service rendered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-11 00:54:14', '2019-09-18 08:23:10', 'en'),
(58, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Questionaires de Webinaire de DNAsbook', 'dnasbook-webinar-questions', '<h4><strong><em>Remarques</em></strong>: <em>Pour acc&eacute;der &agrave; la page d&#39;inscription, vous devez r&eacute;pondre correctement aux questions suivantes:</em></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1) Qu&#39;est-ce que Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) C&#39;est un pays situ&eacute; en Am&eacute;rique.<br />\r\nb) Il s&rsquo;agit d&rsquo;un R&eacute;seau d&rsquo;Entrepreneuriat&nbsp;qui forme ses abonn&eacute;s en eutrepreneuriat et les finance.<br />\r\nc) C&#39;est une association de donateurs am&eacute;ricains qui aide les pauvres dans le&nbsp;monde entier.<br />\r\nd) C&rsquo;est une soci&eacute;t&eacute; am&eacute;ricaine qui aide les gens du monde entier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2) Quelle est la diff&eacute;rence entre &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; et &quot;Opportunity&quot; 4 &quot;&quot;?<br />\r\na) Ils sont les m&ecirc;mes<br />\r\nb) &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; est inclus dans &quot;Opportunit&eacute;&quot; 4 &quot;&quot;.<br />\r\nc) &quot;DNAsbook General&quot;, &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; et &quot;Opportunity&quot; 4 &quot;&quot; sont les&nbsp;m&ecirc;mes, ils traitent les m&ecirc;mes sujets.<br />\r\nd) &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; est une section de &quot;DNAsbook General&quot;. &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot; est r&eacute;serv&eacute; pour l&#39;enseignement de l&#39;entrepreneuriat et au financement. &quot;Opportunity&quot; 4 &quot;est un module de &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing &quot;, il est si important que ce ne serait pas une erreur de le confondre avec &quot;DNAsbook Digital Marketing&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3) Qu&#39;est-ce que la R&egrave;gle 20/20?<br />\r\na) Elle n&#39;est pas si importante dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nb) C&#39;est un secret, personne ne sait ce que c&#39;est.<br />\r\nc) C&#39;est une r&egrave;gle tr&egrave;s importante dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. Vous devez appliquer la R&egrave;gle 20/20 si vous voulez r&eacute;ussir dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nd) C&rsquo;est une r&egrave;gle qui a &eacute;t&eacute; invent&eacute;e et qui a d&eacute;j&agrave; &eacute;t&eacute; utilis&eacute;e dans une autre entreprise, adapt&eacute;e par la suite &agrave; Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4) Pourquoi 4 niveaux de b&eacute;n&eacute;fice dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) Il existe 4 niveaux de b&eacute;n&eacute;fice dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot; pour aider les abonn&eacute;s &agrave; maximiser leurs commissions mensuelles car l&rsquo;objectif de Opportunity &quot;4&quot; est d&rsquo;aider ses abonn&eacute;s financi&egrave;rement tout en les formant en entrepreneuriat.<br />\r\nb) Parce que 4 niveaux ne sont qu&#39;une meilleure fa&ccedil;on de faire les choses.<br />\r\nc) Tout juste&nbsp;pour d&eacute;tourner l&#39;attention de l&#39;objectif principal de Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nd) C&rsquo;est d&rsquo;organiser les choses dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. Pour &ecirc;tre honn&ecirc;te, personne ne sait pourquoi!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5) Comment appliquer la R&egrave;gle 20/20?<br />\r\na) Amenez simplement 40 personnes dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; et vous avez appliqu&eacute; la R&egrave;gle 20/20!<br />\r\nb) Appliquer la R&egrave;gle 20/20 signifie amener 20 personnes dans Opportunit&eacute; &laquo;4&raquo; via votre lien d&rsquo;affili&eacute;&nbsp;et demander &agrave; chacune d&rsquo;entre elles d&rsquo;inscrire&nbsp;dans Opportunit&eacute; &laquo;4&raquo;, &agrave; leur tour, 20 personnes via leurs liens d&rsquo;affili&eacute;s et de s&rsquo;assurer que tout le monde&nbsp;fait la&nbsp;m&ecirc;me chose jusqu&#39;au 4&egrave;me niveau.<br />\r\nc) Parlez&nbsp;de Opportunity &quot;4&quot; avec 20 personnes et demandez &agrave; chacune d&rsquo;elles de parler de Opportunity &quot;4&quot; &agrave; 20 autres personnes, qu&rsquo;elles s&rsquo;abonnent ou non, vous avez appliqu&eacute; la R&egrave;gle 20/20.<br />\r\nd) Appliquer la R&egrave;gle 20/20 signifie inscrire 20 personnes dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; et s&rsquo;arr&ecirc;ter. Vous n&#39;avez rien d&#39;autre &agrave; faire, vous terminez votre travail en tant que distributeur de la formation Opportunity &quot;4&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6) Comment Opportunity &quot;4&quot; paie vos frais?<br />\r\na) Lorsque vous leur envoyez une lettre expliquant que vous &ecirc;tes pauvre, vous ne pouvez pas payer vos frais mensuels et leur dire&nbsp;de ne pas &ecirc;tre gourmand, qu&#39;ils doivent payer vos frais mensuels.<br />\r\nb) En vous envoyant chaque mois un ch&egrave;que clairement libell&eacute;: &quot;Pour vos frais mensuels&quot;.<br />\r\nc) Ne vous inqui&eacute;tez pas, ils l&#39;envoient automatiquement tous les mois. Ils savent que vous n&#39;avez pas d&#39;argent, mais que vous voulez en gagner. Ils sont gentils, ils aident les gens dans le monde entier financi&egrave;rement.<br />\r\nd) &Agrave; partir du moment o&ugrave; vous avez 10 abonn&eacute;s dans votre groupe, du niveau 1 au niveau 4, Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; commencera &agrave;&nbsp;payer vos frais mensuels via vos commissions mensuelles si ces 10 abonn&eacute;s payent leurs frais mensuels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>7) Comment pouvez-vous ne jamais payer les frais mensuels de votre propre poche dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) Cela se produit lorsque vous leur dites que vous souhaitez qu&rsquo;ils vous autorisent &agrave; ne jamais payer de frais mensuels dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. Savez-vous que ce sont des gens gentils, ils vous &eacute;couteront sp&eacute;cialement quand ils vous aiment.<br />\r\nb) Cela se produit lorsque vous inscrivez dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; 20 personnes avant la fin du mois dans lequel vous entrez dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. Et ces 20 personnes doivent &ecirc;tre actives en inscrivant dans&nbsp;Opportunity &quot;4&quot; d&#39;autres personnes et en payant leurs frais mensuels. Si vous faites cela, vous aurez suffisamment de commissions d&egrave;s le 1er mois pour couvrir vos frais mensuels.<br />\r\nc) Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; forme&nbsp;gratuitement en entrepreneuriat et&nbsp;finance aussi gratuitement. Ne vous inqui&eacute;tez pas du paiement de frais mensuels!<br />\r\nd) Il suffit d&rsquo;inscrire dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; 10 personnes au cours de votre premier mois.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8) Qu&#39;est-ce que pluralit&eacute; de&nbsp;comptes dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) C&#39;est pour vous tenir occup&eacute;.<br />\r\nb) C&#39;est pour vous distraire.<br />\r\nc) Ne t&#39;inqui&egrave;te pas! Ce n&#39;est rien!<br />\r\nd) Il y a des d&eacute;fis et des r&eacute;compenses dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. Il existe &quot;pluralit&eacute; de&nbsp;comptes&quot; dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; pour permettre aux abonn&eacute;s d&#39;avoir acc&egrave;s &agrave; de multiples chances, &agrave; des chances illimit&eacute;es&nbsp;de&nbsp;r&eacute;compenses dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. Cela permet &agrave; chacun d&#39;avoir une chance illimit&eacute;e de gagner de l&#39;argent dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;&nbsp;peu importe le moment o&ugrave; vous entrez dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. Il y aura toujours de la place pour tout le monde car les chances de gagner de l&#39;argent dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; sont illimit&eacute;es en raison de cette&nbsp;fonctionnalit&eacute; de &quot;pluralit&eacute; de&nbsp;comptes&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>9) Comment Opportunity &quot;4&quot; fonctionne?<br />\r\na) Il n&#39;y a pas de r&egrave;gles dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nb) Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; a 4 niveaux de profit. En appliquant la R&egrave;gle 20/20, les abonn&eacute;s doivent amener 20 abonn&eacute;s dans le syst&egrave;me et leur demander d&#39;inscrire&nbsp;&eacute;galement 20 abonn&eacute;s dans le syst&egrave;me &agrave; leur tour. Ils&nbsp;doivent&nbsp;s&#39;assurer que ce message est&nbsp;transmis d&#39;abonn&eacute; &agrave; abonn&eacute; jusqu&#39;au 4&egrave;me niveau.<br />\r\nc) Personne ne sait comment fonctionne Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;!<br />\r\nd) Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; n&#39;est qu&#39;une bonne opportunit&eacute;, n&#39;est-ce pas?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>10) Pourquoi des frais mensuels sont-ils inclus dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; est une formation en entrepreneuriat et les abonn&eacute;s sont&nbsp;financ&eacute;s mensuellement. Ce service important comporte des frais mensuels, car les commissions mensuelles proviennent des frais pay&eacute;s par les abonn&eacute;s pour le service rendu. Opportunity &quot;4&quot; d&eacute;cide de partager ces frais avec ses abonn&eacute;s. Les commissions proviennent des frais vers&eacute;s au syst&egrave;me par les&nbsp;abonn&eacute;s pour le&nbsp;service&nbsp;rendu (formation et financement).<br />\r\nb) Nous ne savons pas. Et vous?<br />\r\nc) Le syst&egrave;me doit &ecirc;tre pris en charge. Les abonn&eacute;s ayant de l&#39;argent et g&eacute;n&eacute;reux, ils doivent payer des frais.<br />\r\nd) C&#39;est pour aider les Am&eacute;ricains pauvres.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>11) Comment inscrire des personnes dans votre groupe dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot;?<br />\r\na) Appelez-les et ils viennent &agrave; vous!<br />\r\nb) En leur parlant et en partageant avec eux les bonnes nouvelles quotidiennes d&#39;Am&eacute;rique.<br />\r\nc) Pour inscrire quelqu&#39;un dans votre groupe dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;, vous devez lui donner votre lien d&#39;affili&eacute;. La personne doit cliquer sur votre lien d&#39;affili&eacute;, suivre les instructions et s&#39;inscrire &agrave; la fin. Cette personne sera alors &agrave; votre niveau 1. Les persones &agrave; votre niveau 1 continueront le m&ecirc;me processus &agrave; leur tour jusqu&#39;au niveau 4 avec leur lien d&#39;affili&eacute;.<br />\r\nd) Ne t&#39;inqui&egrave;te pas! Il suffit d&#39;envoyer la personne sur le site!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>12) Sur quels abonn&eacute;s dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; vous &ecirc;tes pay&eacute;?<br />\r\na) Sur tous les abonn&eacute;s de l&#39;ensemble de Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;. Ils vous appartiennent tous.<br />\r\nb) Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot; ne paye pas les abonn&eacute;s uniquement pour les personnes qu&#39;ils inscrivent dans le syst&egrave;me, ils sont &eacute;galement pay&eacute;s pour les abonn&eacute;s que leurs abonn&eacute;s inscrivent dans le syst&egrave;me jusqu&#39;au 4&egrave;me niveau.<br />\r\nc) Il n&#39;y a pas de paiement de commissions dans Opportunit&eacute; &quot;4&quot;.<br />\r\nd) Ils ne vous payent que pour les personnes de votre 1er niveau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>13) Quelles sont les 2 choses que vous devez faire dans Opportunity &quot;4&quot; pour r&eacute;ussir rapidement?<br />\r\na) Abonnez&nbsp;20 personnes et donnez-leur quotidiennement des nouvelles am&eacute;ricaines.<br />\r\nb) Savoir comment parler aux gens de fa&ccedil;on convaincante et payer leurs frais mensuellement.<br />\r\nc) Envoyez des messages WhatSapp &agrave; vos amis sur Opportunity &quot;4&quot; et rien d&rsquo;autre.<br />\r\nd) 1) Appliquez la R&egrave;gle 20/20 en abonnant 20 personnes au syst&egrave;me via votre lien d&#39;affili&eacute;.<br />\r\n2) Demandez-leur d&#39;inscrire&nbsp;&agrave; leur tour 20 personnes dans Opportunity 4 et assurez-vous qu&rsquo;elles transmettent le m&ecirc;me message &agrave; chaque abonn&eacute; jusqu&#39;au 4&egrave;me niveau. Tout le monde doit payer ses frais mensuels dans le syst&egrave;me, car les commissions proviennent des frais vers&eacute;s au syst&egrave;me pour le service rendu.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-11 00:56:12', '2019-10-04 08:19:38', 'fr'),
(59, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'DNAsbook Distributor Training Certificate', 'dnasbook-distributor-training-certificate', '<p>Congratulations! You have passed your <em><strong>Opportunity &quot;4&quot; Distributor Training Test</strong></em>!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fill the form below to be able to print your Certificate on the next page!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"3\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"3\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><em><strong>First &amp; Last Names:</strong></em></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><em><strong>Your Email:</strong></em></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><em><strong>Your Country:</strong></em></td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After you print your certificate on the next page, we will allow you to register in the system, have access to your affiliate link on your dashboard and begin registering people into your group! That will be the beginning of your route towards your financial independance!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>NEXT PAGE &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-11 00:57:08', '2019-09-12 01:09:10', 'en'),
(60, 'PUBLISHED', NULL, 'Certificat de Fin de Formation de Distributeur', 'dnasbook-distributor-training-certificate', '<p>Toutes nos f&eacute;licitations! Vous avez r&eacute;ussi votre test de Formation de Distributeur de Opportunity &quot;4&quot;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remplissez le formulaire ci-dessous pour pouvoir imprimer votre certificat sur&nbsp;la page suivante!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table align=\"left\" border=\"3\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"3\">\r\n	<thead>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope=\"row\"><em>Vos Pr&eacute;nom et Nom de Famille:</em>&nbsp;</th>\r\n			<th scope=\"col\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</thead>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope=\"row\"><em>Votre Email:</em></th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope=\"row\"><em>Votre Pays:</em></th>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apr&egrave;s avoir imprim&eacute; votre certificat sur la page suivante, nous vous permettrons de vous inscrire dans le syst&egrave;me, d&rsquo;avoir acc&egrave;s &agrave; votre lien d&rsquo;affiliation sur votre Tableau de Bord et de commencer &agrave; inscrire des gens&nbsp;dans votre groupe! Ce sera le d&eacute;but de votre parcours vers votre ind&eacute;pendance financi&egrave;re!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>PAGE SUIVANTE &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 1, 'PAGE', 'NO SIDEBAR', '2019-09-11 00:59:16', '2019-10-04 08:36:54', 'fr'),
